<chapter id="core-configuracao">

	<title>Configuração do Signer-Core</title>

	<section>
		<title>Uso do componente</title>
		<para>
			Para utilizar o componente
			<emphasis>Signer-Core</emphasis>
			num projeto Java, 
            basta adicionar a sua dependência no arquivo
			<filename> pom.xml</filename>
			, conforme o seu gerenciador de projetos:
		</para>
		<para>
			<itemizedlist>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						<ulink url="https://maven.apache.org/">Apache-Maven</ulink>
					</para>
					<para>
						<programlisting>
							<![CDATA[
        		<dependency>
				<groupId>org.demoiselle.signer</groupId>
				<artifactId>signer-core</artifactId>
				<version>4.3.0</version>
			</dependency>]]>
						</programlisting>
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						<ulink url="https://buildr.apache.org/">Apache Buildr</ulink>
					</para>
					<para>
						<programlisting>'org.demoiselle.signer:signer-core:jar:4.3.0'</programlisting>
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						<ulink url="http://ant.apache.org/ivy/">Apache Ivy</ulink>
					</para>
					<para>
						<programlisting>
							<![CDATA[<dependency org="org.demoiselle.signer" name="signer-core" rev="4.3.0" />]]>
						</programlisting>
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						<ulink url="http://docs.groovy-lang.org/latest/html/documentation/grape.html">Groovy Grape</ulink>
					</para>
					<para>
						<programlisting>@Grapes(@Grab(group='org.demoiselle.signer', module='signer-core', version='4.3.0')) </programlisting>
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						<ulink url="https://github.com/grails/grails-gradle-plugin">Gradle/Grails</ulink>
					</para>
					<para>
						<programlisting>
							<![CDATA[<dependency org="org.demoiselle.signer" name="signer-core" rev="4.3.0" />]]>
						</programlisting>
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						<ulink url="http://www.scala-sbt.org/">Scala SBT</ulink>
					</para>
					<para>
						<programlisting>libraryDependencies += "org.demoiselle.signer" % "signer-core" % "4.3.0"</programlisting>
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						<ulink url="https://leiningen.org/">Leiningen</ulink>
					</para>
					<para>
						<programlisting>[org.demoiselle.signer/signer-core "4.3.0"]</programlisting>
					</para>
				</listitem>
			</itemizedlist>
		</para>

		<para>
			Caso não esteja utilizando nenhum outro tipo de gerenciador (estava morando numa caverna nos últimos dez anos), pode baixar o .jar do repositório:
			<para>
				<ulink url="https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/demoiselle/signer/signer-core/">https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/demoiselle/signer/signer-core/</ulink>
			</para>

		</para>
	</section>

</chapter>